{"tid":665664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(攬炒) 下一個熊市？羅傑斯：中國將是引爆點","createTime":"2018-05-15T07:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T07:35:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38192f644fb3db92013dbdf51104e7195bda10f7","tid":665664,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"在美國有「商品大王」之稱的羅傑斯（Jim Rogers）日前表示，下一個熊市可能將是他一生中最糟糕的一次，羅傑斯在今（14）日受訪時表示，中國恐將是引爆點。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Stansberry Churchouse》報導，羅傑斯受訪表示，過去美國聯準會（Fed）將利率調降至歷史低，使得全球債務也隨之飆高，而現在隨著Fed開始升息，市場將會出問題。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯認為，過去30年全球債務日益高漲，像是在2008年後的10年間，Fed的資產負債表規模在膨脹了500%，當時還有中國的龐大儲蓄可以應急，拯救全球經濟；但如今中國自己也債台高築，羅傑斯警告，中國面臨破產危機即將到來，它將讓全球熊市變的更加惡化。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯說，我希望我能在下一個熊市中生存下去，因為它會變得非常可怕，並且會變得很糟糕，這將是我一生中最糟糕的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2425421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2425421&d=oxW6gKhhKw4scgCLfX8DVDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d961e992\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2425421&h=930da16e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2425421</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ce8406c3ee77d58204cd1fc236f6b4648ada59","tid":665664,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"講咗十年既支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8d5439555a64e9be1d6ed6b50f874c8a922f22","tid":665664,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"羅傑斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa